::Ender::
       He acts shocked as the shots ping against his plating.  "You're 
absolutely right.  How rude of me.  I must make this right."  He turns back 
to Rodimus Prime and taps him on the shoulder.  "Oh Rody, old chap.  I was 
wondering if I might have the honor of attacking you at the moment.  Oh and 
I'm terribly sorry about shooting at your back earlier, it was horribly 
inconsiderate of me.  I do hope you'll forgive me."  He glances over his 
shoulder at Nightlight.  "Is that better?"  He than fires three more shots at 
her.

--part1_1ac.4977a24.2a552a27_boundary
